#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:planning.planning_shift_notification
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\"/>\n"
"                        You have successfully requested to switch your "
"shift. You will be notified when another employee takes over your shift."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\"/>\n"
"                        ທ່ານໄດ້ສົ່ງຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍປ່ຽນຜັດວຽກສຳເລັດແລ້ວ. "
"ທ່ານຈະໄດ້ຮັບການແຈ້ງເຕືອນເມື່ອມີພະນັກງານຄົນອື່ນມາຮັບຜັດວຽກແທນທ່ານ."

